WEBVTT

00:09:28.544 --> 00:09:30.868
or Twitter and Google and so on.

00:09:30.892 --> 00:09:34.024
They all seem like great people
with good intention --

00:09:34.048 --> 00:09:35.428
let's assume that.

00:09:35.452 --> 00:09:39.127
If you could speak with the leaders
of those companies,

00:09:39.151 --> 00:09:40.442
what would you say to them?

00:09:40.466 --> 00:09:42.235
CA: Well, you know what --

00:09:42.259 --> 00:09:44.603
I'm sure they are
incredibly well-intentioned,

00:09:44.627 --> 00:09:49.845
and they certainly developed
an unbelievable, game-changing system,

00:09:49.869 --> 00:09:53.080
where everybody's connected
on this thing called Facebook.

00:09:53.104 --> 00:09:56.905
And they've created a massive
economy for themselves

00:09:56.929 --> 00:09:59.609
and an amazing amount of income.

00:09:59.633 --> 00:10:00.813
I would just say,